    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294780/extras/e784b803b1ca4c0080641456119949c5.avif?t=1771408666\" width=614 height=96 /></span><br><strong></strong>《背包幸存者》是一款动作游戏，你将与成群的敌人展开对决。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在你的背包里装满武器和物品，变得更强大，在冒险中不断前进。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次冒险后，你都会变得更加强大，并根据自己的游戏风格定制你的角色。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294780/extras/9e58708250698009598f12cc35a469da.webp?t=1771408666\" width=616 height=57 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294780/extras/f6e7090a9667037004b85660c5978cfc.poster.avif?t=1771408666\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294780/extras/f6e7090a9667037004b85660c5978cfc.webm?t=1771408666\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294780/extras/f6e7090a9667037004b85660c5978cfc.mp4?t=1771408666\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong></strong>使用各种强大的武器和物品消灭成群的敌人</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294780/extras/4c45da10c85decba595470cca9cf8c7b.webp?t=1771408666\" width=616 height=57 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294780/extras/d2201ffe2e1706d4c3774ba0f0db0d83.poster.avif?t=1771408666\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/229